  "title": "Project Management Specialist (Office Hours, 5 Days) #HJG",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li><p>Set up and maintain governance structures for all site-level and Business Excellence (BEx) projects.</p></li><li><p>Develop and manage project templates, trackers, schedules, and reporting mechanisms.</p></li><li><p>Track progress of projects including Site Master Plan initiatives, Lean/Six Sigma (Improve stage) projects, and One Plan activities.</p></li><li><p>Monitor timelines, milestones, risks, and action items; escalate issues through appropriate governance channels.</p></li><li><p>Prepare weekly and monthly progress reports, consolidating updates from workstream leads.</p></li><li><p>Support leadership reviews, tier meetings, and project discussions with structured documentation.</p></li><li><p>Coordinate with cross-functional teams to collect updates and maintain accurate project status.</p></li><li><p>Follow up on outstanding actions, decisions, and deliverables.</p></li><li><p>Ensure all project documents (plans, charters, trackers, minutes) are up to date and stored in the correct location.</p></li><li><p>Maintain audit-ready documentation aligned with site and BEx requirements.</p></li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements</strong></p><ul><li><p>Diploma or Degree in Operations, Business, Engineering, or equivalent experience.</p></li><li><p>Familiarity with project management workflows and basic PMO processes.</p></li><li><p>Hands-on experience in project coordination and execution.</p></li><li><p>Experience with Lean/Six Sigma projects is preferred but not mandatory.</p></li><li><p>Comfortable working with spreadsheets, trackers, and structured reporting tools.</p></li><li><p>Able to start work immediately.<br /></p><p>If you are interested in this position, do kindly drop your most updated resume to <a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">joshua.gan@recruitexpress.com.sg</a> and <a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">leonleong@recruitexpress.com.sg</a> (Attn: Project Management Specialist)</p><p>Leon Leong De Cong<br />R1551708<br />Recruit Express Pte Ltd (Healthcare & Lifesciences Division)<br />EA License: 99C4599</p></li></ul>",
